      "level": 2,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Material properties of the existing structure have been determined through a combination of archive drawings, destructive testing (core samples) and non-destructive testing (Schmidt hammer, cover meter). The assessment follows NEN 8700 for existing structures."
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "title": "Existing concrete properties (from core tests)",
          "headers": ["Element", "Cores tested", "f_ck,is [MPa]", "Design class"],
          "rows": [
