            ["Columns upper floors", "4", "24.2", "C20/25 (assessed)"],
            ["Beams all floors", "8", "26.8", "C25/30 (assessed)"],
            ["Precast floor slabs", "4", "32.1", "C28/35 (assessed)"],
            ["Foundation pile caps", "3", "22.5", "C20/25 (assessed)"]
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Reinforcement: QR24 (FeB 240) confirmed from exposed bars. Design yield strength f_yd = 240 / 1.15 = 209 MPa."
        }
